Project: Platformer 4
Student: Logan Barnes (ltbarnes)

Hovercraft (hover ellipsoid) racing game. Perfecting drifting is key. Race through the cyan colored waypoints. Press 'G' to toggle GRAPHICS CARD DESTRUCTION MODE!!! dun dun dun...


Controls:

	 W/S 			- 		move forward/backward
	 A/D			-		turn left/right

	  8				- 		toggle camera lock
	  						(locks camera behind player)

	 +/- 			-  		change camera zoom
	mouse			- 		move camera (when unlocked)

  Backspace 		- 		back to menu

